{"tid":1588893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗大騙子","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:15:19.000Z","uid":203761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78905c271d90be4b3ad7fcdbf2fcadcf2da63440","tid":1588893,"uid":203761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"幫post<br />\n元朗老千大騙子專呃飲呃食洗女人錢<br />\n最中意呃車友幫佢買野     欠債五還錢<br />\n姓名:鄒𢓭兵<br />\n花名:周兵<br />\n電話:68888549<br />\n車牌：NU 236<br />\n地址:元朗崇山新村4區11号 黃榮記再上黃色貨櫃旁的銀色閘門<br />\n<br />\n老豆公司:錦田軍營對面廣泰車房.   鄒廣華<br />\n<br />\n        一齊咁耐以黎洗我既食我既，連旅行錢都係我比。最叻既係賴皮五找數出面差人錢就問我借錢找數，ok當時你係我男朋友當然信任你，之後買名牌野既時候又話冇帶現金叫我比住先，呃左我一萬蚊話幫我出去交錢，結果都係冇交到，到而家2年幾都未還過一蚊。無錢學人買名牌！<br />\n啲衫褲鞋襪全部都係假嘅！最中意帶假錶 帶住隻假朱古力地通拿，充大頭都唔使充咁大😂。人吾笑狗都吠      圖係下邊*<br />\n      成日做埋啲呃呃騙騙嘅嘢不務正業，呃人過數之後就失蹤，苦主一大班 不過呢個世界係有天理既，班苦主報左警之後佢就比警方吿以 欺騙手段獲得他人財產！<br />\n佢邊有錢比反啲苦主，最後我心軟再借錢比個人渣。<br />\n      呢個人渣仲有好多事端唔熟唔食,係自己車會(mk5車會)賣汽車零件，橋唔怕舊最緊要受，用反同一個方法呃人錢 所有人都係過左數之後 收五到貨 佢最叻係拖字訣！<br />\n 最近係[mk6車會]所謂幫人寫電腦，又係用同一個方法去呃人錢，先叫人過數然後拖字訣！圖係下邊*<br />\n一齊左兩年前前後後差我$57500<br />\n1蚊都冇還過 <br />\n所有圖在下邊<br />\n希望各位車友吾好再中伏<br />\n#人無恥則無敵<br />\n#臉皮幾十尺厚<br />\n#唔好嫌棄我打到一嚿嚿<br />\n之前已經比人放過上連登:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/6706589/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F6706589%2Fpage%2F1&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=94a70c3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/6706589/page/1</a><br />\n******以下圖片係老千 大家要小心******<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymb2L1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fymb2L1K.jpg&h=250cafb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zN0nL1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzN0nL1N.jpg&h=bddd2847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJgQtt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJgQtt.jpg&h=fd67bb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwMijmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwMijmP.jpg&h=bcd2d119&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c7484effbeb678796fc93fd29c7abe6f89b90859","tid":1588893,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"213570275b5ab89159565d428459c1bb78750273","tid":1588893,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"b034b0c580c836c06312e97a42355e58ecddff23","tid":1588893,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"8087adf4b484f64413ccccc80f2969d29eefb877","tid":1588893,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"fc81d2eb68e8ac905559bff6dc5c208c2120f34b","tid":1588893,"uid":165339,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都食到軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2989e156ca153a154b11e197e08cc5ba7a4ec19c","tid":1588893,"uid":200466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"對樓主無惡意 但咁既樣都昆到人 樓主下次眼光要高返啲"},{"pid":"d